üß† End-of-Day Reflection
Aaj maine AI ke saath kaam karte hue bohot kuch seekha. Pehle, maine realize kiya ke AI ek tool hai, replacement nahi 
mujhe har output ko critically evaluate karna zaroori hai aur blindly trust nahi karna chahiye. Maine dekha ke AI mere
repetitive tasks ko handle karke mujhe creative work ke liye zyada time deta hai, jo meri actual value add karta hai.
Mujhe ye bhi samajh aaya ke AI se best results lene ke liye clear aur specific prompts dena important hai, aur jitna better
main communicate karunga utna better output milega. Sabse badi learning ye rahi ke AI collaboration ek partnership hai jahan 
main apni human judgment, creativity, aur ethical thinking ko AI ki speed aur efficiency ke saath combine kar sakta hoon to
achieve better results.
